=== Live-Coding practice exercises

The TopLap crew has some basic resources for learning to live-code, including
practice ideas.  It would be nice to expand on this list and put together a
good sequence of exercises that could be followed to go from 100% newbie to jam
ready beginner.

==== Sonification
* sonify basic algorithms

==== Algorithmic Composition
* markov models
* l-systems
* trees
* grammars

==== Recovering from errors
* deal with compile errors
* runtime errors
* full crash

